<ab facs="#facs_570_r2l6">ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell ʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> an der ſtett 
<add><ab facs="#facs_570_r2l5">
<del rend="strikethrough">eıne </del></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> dıe Jr </del> eine dıe Jr in <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_570_r2l8">benennet habt . von ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe Jr mıt vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_570_r2l7">habt </ab></add> ʒu reden 
<del rend="strikethrough">habt </del> etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_570_r2l9">haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd wellen <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu lıeb alſo <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_570_r2l10">gen kıcʒing / 
<del rend="strikethrough">auf </del> von heẅt v̈ber vııȷ tag / das ıſt der ſamſtag vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_570_r2l11">anthonij ſchıerıſt ʒu nacht / Ob es <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell auf <expan>dıeſ<ex>elbe</ex></expan> ʒeıt auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_570_r2l12">füklıch ıſt dahin ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . vnd vns <expan>daʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> tut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_570_r2l13"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> es aber <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell auf <expan>dıeſ<ex>elbe</ex></expan> ʒeıt niht füklıch . wenn Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_570_r2l14">denn darnach <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> tag gen kıcʒıng beſchaıdt . vnd vns den ſo ʒeıtlıch </ab>
