</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_570" id="284r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                        Bickembach, <expan>burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Miltemberg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, etwern von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        edell zu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> an der stett eine, die ir in
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> benennet habt, von sache
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die ir mit uns <add>habt</add> zu reden,
                        etc., das haben wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und wellen
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu lieb also
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> gen Kiczing von hewt über viii tag, das
                        ist der <app><note><q type="date">samstag vor Anthonii</q>16.01.1423</note></app>, schierist zu nacht, ob es
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell auf
                            <expan>dies<ex>elbe</ex></expan> zeit auch füklich ist, dahin zu
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, und uns
                            <expan>dazwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> tut. <expan>W<ex>er</ex>e</expan> es aber
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell auf
                            <expan>dies<ex>elbe</ex></expan> zeit niht füklich, wenn ir uns denn
                        darnach <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> tag gen Kiczing beschaidt und uns den
                        so zeitlich bevor <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündt</expan>, daz wir das erlangen
                        mugen, so wellen wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell dahin
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>; denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Erhardi. </ab>
</div>
